                        Buying Registered stories

Did you like what you saw in this demo? If you did then no doubt you will be
anxious to get your hands on some more stories. Well this is easily done.
Just send me £7.50 (including £1.50 p+p) per story that you require and as
soon as any cheques have cleared, I will despatch your programs by first
class post. If you live outside of the UK then please add an extra 50 pence
to cover postage.

If you live in the UK you can, if you wish, send me a stamped addressed
jiffy bag (large enough to contain the amount of disks you have ordered)
along with your order, in which case you only need pay £5.00.

